getRoundData(uint80).notice: get data about a round. Consumers are encouraged to check that they're receiving fresh data by inspecting the updatedAt and answeredInRound return values. getTimestamp(uint256).notice: get block timestamp when an answer was last updated

latestAnswer().notice: Reads the current answer from aggregator delegated to.

latestTimestamp().notice: Reads the last updated height from aggregator delegated to.
